refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public boolReflectionEnum::isBacked
回退 Enum 是具有本地 string 和 int 回退标量值。 并非所有枚举都是回退的。

  &reftitle.examples;



    ReflectionEnum::isBacked 例子


<?php
enum Suit
{
    case Hearts;
    case Diamonds;
    case Clubs;
    case Spades;
}

enum BackedSuit: string
{
    case Hearts = 'H';
    case Diamonds = 'D';
    case Clubs = 'C';
    case Spades = 'S';
}

var_dump((new ReflectionEnum(Suit::class))->isBacked());
var_dump((new ReflectionEnum(BackedSuit::class))->isBacked());
?>


    &example.outputs;


bool(false)
bool(true)
